Class Product

  • java.lang.Object
    • brien.Product
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Item
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AudioPlayer, MoviePlayer, Widget

    public abstract class Product
extends java.lang.Object
implements Item
    Product.java - This abstract class is used to define methods that will be used by classes that inherit from it. It is designed to have all of the basic information and functionality that all products will need.
